{
  "stem": "4710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, whatever we regarded as kosher was a basic food, which is-- which don't have to be kosher.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was not a specific Jewish shop.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents and six children, one girl and five boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was fifth.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was one but the youngest.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At 1944-- I mean, when we were deported, my oldest brother was 22.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My sister was 21.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then 19, 16, 14, and 11.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 14.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it means that I got-- I got the like cast-over clothes from the older brothers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a disadvantage.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I very rarely got something new.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's not-- no advantage, because I was not the youngest, I should be called the little favorite.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm not-- nevertheless, I was down on the line.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I was not-- I couldn't remember any advantage being number five.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very close.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very loving.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] With the extended family, I had a great aunt living with us, my grandfather's maiden sister.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, at the same time, we had-- we had uncles and aunts, a lot of cousins.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Quite a-- quite a large family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "One of the largest families in our town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wouldn't say all, but quite a number of them lived in Kapuvar.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Usually my-- from the paternal side, Abeleszes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was-- there was four Abeleszes in Kapuvar besides my father.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was very naughty.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's-- that's how I remember.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was always-- I was very good in school, in the subject of studying.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I was very misbehaved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the usual things, scrounging apples from next door and making fun of the teacher when he was not looking.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sometimes I got caught and then I got a good telling off.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I loved fun and I loved sports.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
